Package com.mygdx.othello.models

Class GameData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mygdx.othello.models.GameData
  • public class GameData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages the loading of the game data into minimalist variables The values of the said variables are then extracted by the Board constructor to launch a game
